Package: agrupaVariables
Type: Package
Title: group values of ordinal varibles according to a target variable 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Gabriela Plantié
Maintainer: The package maintainer <glplantie@gmail.com>
Description: creates groups for ordinal variables trying to join values that are similar according to its correlation with the target. In this case is using the probability of the sample belonging to the union of that sample and the previous one applying an hypergeometric test. 
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
Imports: dplyr
Suggests: testthat
